usage: config_diff.py [-h] --old-dir OLD_DIR --new-dir NEW_DIR [--json-output]
                      [--format {markdown,json}]

Compare two conf.d/ directories — per-tenant blast radius report

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --old-dir OLD_DIR     Baseline config directory
  --new-dir NEW_DIR     New/staged config directory
  --json-output         Output JSON instead of Markdown
  --format {markdown,json}
                        Output format (default: markdown). Alias: --json-
                        output is equivalent to --format json

Examples:
  config_diff.py --old-dir conf.d.baseline --new-dir conf.d/
  config_diff.py --old-dir conf.d.baseline --new-dir conf.d/ --json-output
